\[\nabla_{\eta_{i}}\mathcal{J}_{\Lambda,i}(\bm{\theta},\eta_{i})=\mathop{\mathbb{ E}}_{\tau\sim p_{\Lambda}(\cdot|\bm{\theta})}\left[\nabla_{\eta_{i}}f_{i}(C_{i}( \tau),\eta_{i})\right]+\nabla_{\eta_{i}}g_{i}(\eta_{i}).\] (67)

