\[\nabla_{\eta_{i}}\mathcal{J}_{\Lambda,i}(\bm{\theta},\eta_{i})=\mathop{\mathbb{ E}}_{\tau\sim p_{\Lambda}(\cdot|\bm{\theta})}\left[-2\kappa_{i}C_{i}(\tau) \right]+2\kappa_{i}\eta_{i}.\] (68)Considering the behavior of C-PGAE described in Section 4, we obtain the following sample-based version:

